=head1 Advanced Testing

=over 7

=item * Skipping Test

  $ perl -t skip.t

=item * Testing Object-Oriented Features

  $ perl -t ooo.t

=item * Grouping Tests

  $ perl -t groupings.t

=item * Testing Large Strings

  $ perl -t large_strings.t

=item * Testing Files

  $ perl -t files.t

=item * Testing STDOUT or STDERR

  $ perl -t output.t

=item * Using Mock Objects

  $ perl -t mock.t

=item * Writing Our Own Test::* Modules

  $ perl -t -Ilib custom_modules.t

=back

=cut
